OL,3,CGP surgeries in England to advertise
OL,4,CJess's Rule to prevent avoidable deaths
OL,6,FA new system which requires family
OL,7,Fdoctors to think again if a patient
OL,8,Fhas had three appointments for their
OL,9,Fsymptoms with no diagnosis will be
OL,10,Fadvertised in all GP practices across
OL,11,FEngland from this week.
OL,13,FThe requirement is called Jess's Rule
OL,14,Fand is named after 27-year-old Jessica
OL,15,FBrady, who contacted her surgery 20
OL,16,Ftimes before she died from cancer in
OL,17,F2020, without a diagnosis.
