OL,3,CGP surgeries in England to advertise
OL,4,CJess's Rule to prevent avoidable deaths
OL,6,FIt was rolled out in September to
OL,7,Fprevent avoidable deaths and help
OL,8,Fmedics avoid missing serious illnesses
OL,9,Fsuch as cancer.
OL,11,FJess's Rule also urges GPs to think
OL,12,Fagain if a patient still has not
OL,13,Freceived a diagnosis and their
OL,14,Fsymptoms have worsened.
OL,16,FThey are encouraged to consider a
OL,17,Fsecond opinion, see patients face-to-
OL,18,Fface for physical examinations, or
OL,19,Forder more tests.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
