OL,3,CGP surgeries in England to advertise
OL,4,CJess's Rule to prevent avoidable deaths
OL,6,FMs Brady's mother Andrea Brady, said
OL,7,Fthe charity set up in her daughter's
OL,8,Fname has been "heartened" by the
OL,9,Fresponse from primary care to the
OL,10,F"three strikes and rethink" approach.
OL,12,FPosters advertising Jess's Rule have
OL,13,Fbeen distributed to all 6,170 GP
OL,14,Fpractices in England.
OL,16,FDisplaying them will boost patient
OL,17,Fsafety by urging family doctors to
OL,18,Fchallenge their initial assumptions,
OL,19,Faccording to the Department of Health
OL,20,Fand Social Care.
