OL,3,CGP surgeries in England to advertise
OL,4,CJess's Rule to prevent avoidable deaths
OL,6,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting said:
OL,7,F"Every patient deserves to be heard,
OL,8,Fand every serious illness deserves to
OL,9,Fbe caught early.
OL,11,F"Jess's Rule makes that possible `
OL,12,Freminding clinicians to take a fresh
OL,13,Flook when symptoms persist, and
OL,14,Fempowering patients to speak up about
OL,15,Ftheir care.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
