OL,4,CJess's Rule to prevent avoidable deaths
OL,6,F"This is a fitting tribute to Jessica
OL,7,FBrady and the tireless campaigning of
OL,8,Fher parents. Their determination to
OL,9,Fturn tragedy into lasting change will
OL,10,Fhelp protect patients and save lives
OL,11,Ffor years to come."
OL,13,FThe posters were designed by the DHSC,
OL,14,FNHS England and Jess's parents Andrea
OL,15,Fand Simon Brady.
OL,17,FGP surgeries will also receive a
OL,18,Fletter from Mr Streeting and NHS
OL,19,FEngland's national medical director Dr
OL,20,FClaire Fuller to stress the importance
OL,21,Fof Jess's Rule.
