OL,3,CGP surgeries in England to advertise
OL,4,CJess's Rule to prevent avoidable deaths
OL,6,FMs Brady, an engineer for Airbus,
OL,7,Fcontacted her GP surgery around 20
OL,8,Ftimes over six months in the lead up
OL,9,Fto her death in 2020, reporting
OL,10,Fsymptoms such as abdominal pain,
OL,11,Fcoughing, vomiting and weight loss.
OL,13,FDue to restrictions during the
OL,14,Fpandemic she was offered virtual
OL,15,Fappointments and prescribed
OL,16,Fmedications including antibiotics and
OL,17,Fsteroids. She was also told she may be
OL,18,Fsuffering from long Covid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
