OL,4,CJess's Rule to prevent avoidable deaths
OL,6,FMs Brady was finally diagnosed with
OL,7,Fcancer that had spread throughout her
OL,8,Fbody ` but only after her mother paid
OL,9,Ffor her to see a doctor privately. She
OL,10,Fdied in hospital three weeks later.
OL,12,FAndrea Brady said: "Throughout her
OL,13,Fillness, Jess showed a quiet
OL,14,Fdetermination that her experience
OL,15,Fshould lead to meaningful change,
OL,16,Finspiring the launch of Jess's Rule in
OL,17,FSeptember last year. I am so
OL,18,Fincredibly proud of my caring and
OL,19,Fcourageous daughter.
