OL,6,F"The Jessica Brady CEDAR Trust, the
OL,7,Fcharity established in Jess's name,
OL,8,Fhas been heartened by the response
OL,9,Ffrom primary care practitioners
OL,10,Fadopting 'the Three Strikes and We
OL,11,FRethink' approach.
OL,13,F"Many have committed to developing
OL,14,Ffurther training, while others have
OL,15,Fwritten to patients to endorse the
OL,16,Finitiative and show their support.
OL,17,FThis level of engagement has been
OL,18,Fprofoundly encouraging.
