OL,6,F"Jess's Rule posters have now been
OL,7,Fdistributed to all GP practices in
OL,8,FEngland and are expected to be
OL,9,Fdisplayed in consultation rooms.
OL,11,F"By supporting clinicians to take a
OL,12,Ffresh eyes approach when a patient
OL,13,Freturns for a third time with the same
OL,14,For worsening symptoms, Jess's Rule
OL,15,Faims to ensure serious illnesses,
OL,16,Fincluding cancer, are identified and
OL,17,Ftreated earlier ` a goal I remain
OL,18,Fhopeful will be achieved."
OL,26,@nD@AOUzD@ZO]
