OL,6,FDr Fuller said: "Encouraging GP teams
OL,7,Fto challenge a diagnosis when it
OL,8,Fmatters most could save lives by
OL,9,Favoiding missed or late diagnoses, and
OL,10,FI'd like to thank Andrea and Simon
OL,11,FBrady and the Jessica Brady CEDAR
OL,12,FTrust for funding and providing their
OL,13,Fimportant insights to develop the
OL,14,Fposters."
OL,16,FProfessor Victoria Tzortziou Brown,
OL,17,Fchairwoman of the Royal College of
OL,18,FGPs, said that Ms Brady's story "is an
OL,19,Fimportant reminder that sometimes a
OL,20,Frare diagnosis could be the right
OL,21,Fdiagnosis".
