OL,6,FShe added: "Jess's Rule formalises
OL,7,F'best practice' in general practice
OL,8,Fand underlines the importance of
OL,9,Ftaking time to reflect and review a
OL,10,Fdiagnosis, if a treatment plan doesn't
OL,11,Fseem to be working.
OL,13,F"This might mean having a more in-
OL,14,Fdepth conversation with the patient to
OL,15,Fsee what other factors could be
OL,16,Fimpacting their health, asking a
OL,17,Fcolleague for a second opinion, or if
OL,18,Fappropriate, making a referral to
OL,19,Fsecondary care.
