OL,6,F"Timely diagnosis can mean better
OL,7,Foutcomes for patients ` but many
OL,8,Fserious conditions, including many
OL,9,Fcancers, are challenging to identify
OL,10,Fin primary care because the symptoms
OL,11,Fare often similar to other less
OL,12,Fserious and more common conditions.
OL,14,F"The college has worked with Jess
OL,15,FBrady's family and the Jessica Brady
OL,16,FCEDAR Trust to develop learning
OL,17,Fresources for GPs on diagnosing cancer
OL,18,Fin younger people."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUzD@SO]
