OL,6,FResearch by Nuffield Trust and the
OL,7,FHealth Foundation found that half of
OL,8,F16 to 24-year-olds required three or
OL,9,Fmore interactions with a GP surgery
OL,10,Fbefore being diagnosed with cancer,
OL,11,Fcompared with one-in-five across the
OL,12,Fpopulation.
